UFFDAH(Universal Foreign File and Disk Access Helper)

uffdah is an application to manage usb-disks/flash attached to the USB OTG port (if supported) as well as networked fileservers like windows, mac and linux.

the UI will enable creating connections to remote fileservers with login/password/path information stored in a db.

USB attached FS will be discovered via USB Gadget and partitions listed with partition type and mount location preferences

All FS will be mounted off the /media/external tree.



